{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-detail-tsx","path":"/detail/2a5503bf-4c05-5301-82f8-ca1670eb4060","result":{"pageContext":{"html":"<h2>前言</h2>\n<p><code>Node.js</code>是作为一个前端开发者必备的技术栈。</p>\n<p>正如官方中说的那样，<code>Node.js</code>是一个基于 Chrome V8 引擎的 JavaScript 运行时。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Node.js® is a JavaScript runtime built on <a href=\"https://v8.dev/\">Chrome's V8 JavaScript engine</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><code>Node.js</code>让 JavaScript 代码可以脱离浏览器，在其他环境运行，这也是前端工程化的基础</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/90dbc981bbc734f826979dc381b55600/5a190/2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.24324324324324%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/90dbc981bbc734f826979dc381b55600/fcda8/2.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/90dbc981bbc734f826979dc381b55600/12f09/2.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/90dbc981bbc734f826979dc381b55600/e4a3f/2.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/90dbc981bbc734f826979dc381b55600/fcda8/2.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/90dbc981bbc734f826979dc381b55600/5a190/2.png 800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>环境安装</h2>\n<p>进入<code>node.js</code>官方 <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/\">https://nodejs.org/en/</a> ，他会自动根据你的环境推荐安装包。<code>windows</code>环境推荐选择<code>.msi</code>后缀的安装文件，安装过程就是一路确定到底就可以了。<code>mac</code>推荐使用<code>HomeBrew</code>下载<del>HomeBrew 真香</del></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0a911889e1aacad57e23a6727ede8b77/d0143/1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.21621621621621%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0a911889e1aacad57e23a6727ede8b77/fcda8/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0a911889e1aacad57e23a6727ede8b77/12f09/1.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0a911889e1aacad57e23a6727ede8b77/e4a3f/1.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0a911889e1aacad57e23a6727ede8b77/fcda8/1.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0a911889e1aacad57e23a6727ede8b77/efc66/1.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0a911889e1aacad57e23a6727ede8b77/d0143/1.png 1025w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>安装成功后，打开一个终端，windows 上可以选择<code>cmd</code>或<code>powershell</code> ,输入</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">node -v\n</code></pre>\n<p>如果有 node 版本结果，则安装成功。</p>\n<p>具体步骤：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>按住 win+R</li>\n<li>输入 <code>cmd</code> 或者 <code>powershell</code></li>\n<li>输入<code>node -v</code></li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 454px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/39de564a567b10a39db2078a0fa82831/b3c1d/3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 69.5945945945946%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/39de564a567b10a39db2078a0fa82831/b3c1d/3.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/39de564a567b10a39db2078a0fa82831/12f09/3.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/39de564a567b10a39db2078a0fa82831/e4a3f/3.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/39de564a567b10a39db2078a0fa82831/b3c1d/3.png 454w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 454px) 100vw, 454px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>初次使用</h2>\n<p>试试直接在终端中直接输入<code>node</code>，就会进入这个界面。这是 node.js 交互式解释器，可能用过<code>python</code>的同学就会有点熟悉了。我们可以直接输入<code>JavaScript</code>代码并执行，而不需要浏览器环境。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 534px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/fa1c8966539233ddf8476423188fa955/a07a7/4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32.43243243243243%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/fa1c8966539233ddf8476423188fa955/a07a7/4.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/fa1c8966539233ddf8476423188fa955/12f09/4.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/fa1c8966539233ddf8476423188fa955/e4a3f/4.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/fa1c8966539233ddf8476423188fa955/a07a7/4.png 534w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 534px) 100vw, 534px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 576px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/ae8a0172904f5da2811f228db6492b80/533c1/5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.72972972972974%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/ae8a0172904f5da2811f228db6492b80/533c1/5.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/ae8a0172904f5da2811f228db6492b80/12f09/5.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/ae8a0172904f5da2811f228db6492b80/e4a3f/5.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/ae8a0172904f5da2811f228db6492b80/533c1/5.png 576w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>和<code>python</code>类似，我们不仅可以这样一行一行执行，也可以用来执行一个 JavaScript 文件，我们可以通过在终端中执行<code>node &#x3C;文件名></code>来执行文件，或者使用 vs code 中的 插件<code>Code Runner</code>来运行。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 340px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/c2468faf5b9d4f6a4ba3dd73d6db3066/9f933/6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.02702702702703%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/c2468faf5b9d4f6a4ba3dd73d6db3066/9f933/6.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/c2468faf5b9d4f6a4ba3dd73d6db3066/12f09/6.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/c2468faf5b9d4f6a4ba3dd73d6db3066/e4a3f/6.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/c2468faf5b9d4f6a4ba3dd73d6db3066/9f933/6.png 340w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 340px) 100vw, 340px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>node 环境和浏览器环境的区别</h2>\n<p>node 环境中的少了浏览器中的一些 api，像<code>document</code>,<code>window</code>,<code>alert</code>,<code>history</code>都是不支持的。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 506px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/a7edca809a1cabb08cc789645c86bd1c/29f4e/7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49.32432432432432%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/a7edca809a1cabb08cc789645c86bd1c/29f4e/7.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/a7edca809a1cabb08cc789645c86bd1c/12f09/7.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/a7edca809a1cabb08cc789645c86bd1c/e4a3f/7.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/a7edca809a1cabb08cc789645c86bd1c/29f4e/7.png 506w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 506px) 100vw, 506px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>但是它也增加了许多特性。像 I/O 读写和模块加载之类的东西。</p>\n<p>这是使用 node.js 读取文本文件。<del>这就比用 C 语言简单多了</del></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e016b69dc0ab5d9a081f9b59922b7a6c/29c1d/8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.810810810810814%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e016b69dc0ab5d9a081f9b59922b7a6c/fcda8/8.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e016b69dc0ab5d9a081f9b59922b7a6c/12f09/8.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e016b69dc0ab5d9a081f9b59922b7a6c/e4a3f/8.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e016b69dc0ab5d9a081f9b59922b7a6c/fcda8/8.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e016b69dc0ab5d9a081f9b59922b7a6c/efc66/8.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e016b69dc0ab5d9a081f9b59922b7a6c/c83ae/8.png 1180w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e016b69dc0ab5d9a081f9b59922b7a6c/29c1d/8.png 1375w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>什么是 npm</h2>\n<p>npm<del>是\"您配吗\",呸</del> 是 Node Package Manager，也就是 Node 的包管理器。</p>\n<p>了解过<code>python</code>的同学可能知道<code>pip</code>，<code>npm</code>和他有点类似。但是 pip 的包下载后是全局的，npm 可以将依赖（或者称它为包）可以下载到工作区或者下载到全局。</p>\n<p>一般来说，安装了<code>node</code>后，<code>npm</code>也安装好了。可以使用<code>npm -v</code>确认一下。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 278px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/eac43f64e7c4ae9caeb07ab2d4ec2195/4e29d/9.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.24324324324324%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/eac43f64e7c4ae9caeb07ab2d4ec2195/4e29d/9.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/eac43f64e7c4ae9caeb07ab2d4ec2195/12f09/9.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/eac43f64e7c4ae9caeb07ab2d4ec2195/4e29d/9.png 278w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 278px) 100vw, 278px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>npm 官网</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/\">https://www.npmjs.com/</a></p>\n<p>npm 是世界上最大的包管理<del>不是我瞎说的，官网写的</del>。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/9e594ca622b50f7817c1952088f12454/52576/10.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72.97297297297297%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/9e594ca622b50f7817c1952088f12454/fcda8/10.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/9e594ca622b50f7817c1952088f12454/12f09/10.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/9e594ca622b50f7817c1952088f12454/e4a3f/10.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/9e594ca622b50f7817c1952088f12454/fcda8/10.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/9e594ca622b50f7817c1952088f12454/efc66/10.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/9e594ca622b50f7817c1952088f12454/c83ae/10.png 1180w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/9e594ca622b50f7817c1952088f12454/52576/10.png 1412w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Relied upon by more than 11 million developers worldwide, npm is committed to making JavaScript development elegant, productive, and safe. The free npm Registry has become the center of JavaScript code sharing, and with more than one million packages, the largest software registry in the world. Our other tools and services take the Registry, and the work you do around it, to the next level.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>我们也可以在这上边寻找我们一些其他人的造好的轮子，像一些前端开发框架的脚手架<code>@vue/cli</code>,<code>create-react-app</code>之类的，还有 node.js 后端框架<code>express</code>,<code>koa</code>,<code>egg</code>之类的，以及一些其他好用的工具。</p>\n<h2>一些其他的包管理</h2>\n<p><code>npm</code>也有一些令人诟病的地方，像安装速度慢，依赖关系树，镜像以及其他之类的问题，因此出现了一些其他的 node 的包管理器，像<code>cnpm</code> ,<code>yarn</code> 之类的，可以去了解一下。</p>\n<h2>package.json</h2>\n<p>这是一个 node 项目或者说是一个 npm 包的必备的文件。它包含了项目的必要的信息，以及这个项目所依赖的一些的依赖。</p>\n<p>在终端中进入项目所在的目录，输入<code>npm init -y</code>\n就可以一键生成配置文件。\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/5f861273deffe709f9b6d6bd6349ec05/23296/11.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/5f861273deffe709f9b6d6bd6349ec05/fcda8/11.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/5f861273deffe709f9b6d6bd6349ec05/12f09/11.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/5f861273deffe709f9b6d6bd6349ec05/e4a3f/11.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/5f861273deffe709f9b6d6bd6349ec05/fcda8/11.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/5f861273deffe709f9b6d6bd6349ec05/23296/11.png 675w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>一些重要的字段像<code>scripts</code>,<code>dependencies</code>,<code>devDependencies</code>有必要了解。</p>\n<p>可以参考这个， <a href=\"https://javascript.ruanyifeng.com/nodejs/packagejson.html\">https://javascript.ruanyifeng.com/nodejs/packagejson.html</a></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>字段名</th>\n<th>作用</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>scripts</td>\n<td>指定了运行脚本命令的 npm 命令行缩写，比如 start 指定了运行<code>npm run start</code>时，所要执行的命令</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>dependencies</td>\n<td>指定了项目运行所依赖的模块</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>devDependencies</td>\n<td>指定项目开发所需要的模块</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2>如何使用 node.js 过滤问卷名单</h2>\n<p>这就当是一个简单的使用 node.js 的例子吧。我们的寒假项目需要非科协的同学填写问卷，但是有科协的同学填写了问卷，这时我们就需要过滤人员的名单。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/090ee217ffa80360240257260b54ce75/c1c45/12.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 119.59459459459461%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/090ee217ffa80360240257260b54ce75/fcda8/12.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/090ee217ffa80360240257260b54ce75/12f09/12.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/090ee217ffa80360240257260b54ce75/e4a3f/12.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/090ee217ffa80360240257260b54ce75/fcda8/12.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/090ee217ffa80360240257260b54ce75/c1c45/12.png 824w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>我们简单看一下这个需求，我们需要读取一个 excel，然后过滤\"隔壁软软-钟敏睿\"，重新生成一个新的 excel。</p>\n<p>那么我们怎么使用 node.js 读取 excel 呢。首先作为一个<del>调包侠，呸</del> 优秀的程序员，我们需要去看一下有什么其他大佬写好的代码可以用。我使用的是<a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/node-xlsx\">node-xlsx</a></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2207f59f9bc8df4e0d88ee37d4a6bd7b/4a70a/13.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.72972972972974%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2207f59f9bc8df4e0d88ee37d4a6bd7b/fcda8/13.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2207f59f9bc8df4e0d88ee37d4a6bd7b/12f09/13.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2207f59f9bc8df4e0d88ee37d4a6bd7b/e4a3f/13.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2207f59f9bc8df4e0d88ee37d4a6bd7b/fcda8/13.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2207f59f9bc8df4e0d88ee37d4a6bd7b/efc66/13.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2207f59f9bc8df4e0d88ee37d4a6bd7b/c83ae/13.png 1180w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2207f59f9bc8df4e0d88ee37d4a6bd7b/4a70a/13.png 2390w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>我们进入项目后，执行<code>npm install --save node-xlsx</code></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0693a394cb0e81e8e7f5d8bba5de7343/5440e/14.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.16216216216216%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0693a394cb0e81e8e7f5d8bba5de7343/fcda8/14.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0693a394cb0e81e8e7f5d8bba5de7343/12f09/14.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0693a394cb0e81e8e7f5d8bba5de7343/e4a3f/14.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0693a394cb0e81e8e7f5d8bba5de7343/fcda8/14.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0693a394cb0e81e8e7f5d8bba5de7343/efc66/14.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0693a394cb0e81e8e7f5d8bba5de7343/c83ae/14.png 1180w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0693a394cb0e81e8e7f5d8bba5de7343/5440e/14.png 1419w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>首先，我们拿到了问卷填写人员的名单。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/12e50969b7b78bb14caca313e433cd8e/eb2af/15.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64.1891891891892%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/12e50969b7b78bb14caca313e433cd8e/fcda8/15.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/12e50969b7b78bb14caca313e433cd8e/12f09/15.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/12e50969b7b78bb14caca313e433cd8e/e4a3f/15.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/12e50969b7b78bb14caca313e433cd8e/fcda8/15.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/12e50969b7b78bb14caca313e433cd8e/efc66/15.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/12e50969b7b78bb14caca313e433cd8e/eb2af/15.png 954w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>再根据 node-xlsx 的文档，写出代码。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/cd8db89565fff20674b2e52ec424c18b/12e1b/16.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.72972972972974%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/cd8db89565fff20674b2e52ec424c18b/fcda8/16.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/cd8db89565fff20674b2e52ec424c18b/12f09/16.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/cd8db89565fff20674b2e52ec424c18b/e4a3f/16.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/cd8db89565fff20674b2e52ec424c18b/fcda8/16.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/cd8db89565fff20674b2e52ec424c18b/efc66/16.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/cd8db89565fff20674b2e52ec424c18b/c83ae/16.png 1180w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/cd8db89565fff20674b2e52ec424c18b/12e1b/16.png 1607w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>。</p>\n<p>运行<code>node index.js</code>，就得到了我们要的东西。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/9d8a3be7e13ba1e9d1b341c7446cd8fe/21482/17.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.70270270270271%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/9d8a3be7e13ba1e9d1b341c7446cd8fe/fcda8/17.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/9d8a3be7e13ba1e9d1b341c7446cd8fe/12f09/17.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/9d8a3be7e13ba1e9d1b341c7446cd8fe/e4a3f/17.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/9d8a3be7e13ba1e9d1b341c7446cd8fe/fcda8/17.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/9d8a3be7e13ba1e9d1b341c7446cd8fe/efc66/17.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/9d8a3be7e13ba1e9d1b341c7446cd8fe/c83ae/17.png 1180w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/9d8a3be7e13ba1e9d1b341c7446cd8fe/21482/17.png 1350w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>。</p>\n<p>到这里，我们就实现了需求，这只是冰山一角，node.js 能做的事情还很多。</p>\n<h2>如何运行别人的 node 项目</h2>\n<p>我们将代码上传至 GitHub 时，一般都会将依赖之类的文件添加进<code>.gitignore</code>。所以每次 clone 一个 node 项目我们都需要重新下载依赖。例如，上面的那个过滤问卷名单的例子 🌰，我已经将代码放到了 GitHub 上。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/ChenKS12138/node-demo-tutorial\">https://github.com/ChenKS12138/node-demo-tutorial</a></p>\n<p>我们 clone 了这个仓库后，文件目录应该如下，没有<code>node_modules</code>。因此我们需要下载依赖。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>.\n├── README.md\n├── data\n│ └── source.xlsx\n├── index.js\n├── package-lock.json\n└── package.json</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>运行<code>npm install</code>就可以下载依赖了。</p>\n<h2>结语</h2>\n<p>node 能做的事情还很多，这个只是一小部分。至此，你已经打开的新世界的大门。</p>","id":"2a5503bf-4c05-5301-82f8-ca1670eb4060","headings":[{"value":"前言","depth":2},{"value":"环境安装","depth":2},{"value":"初次使用","depth":2},{"value":"node 环境和浏览器环境的区别","depth":2},{"value":"什么是 npm","depth":2},{"value":"npm 官网","depth":2},{"value":"一些其他的包管理","depth":2},{"value":"package.json","depth":2},{"value":"如何使用 node.js 过滤问卷名单","depth":2},{"value":"如何运行别人的 node 项目","depth":2},{"value":"结语","depth":2}],"date":"Tuesday, January 14, 2020 9:14 PM","tags":["JavaScript","Node.js"],"title":"Node.js入门指北"}}}